    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header display-4 text-center">
        About Wecasual
      </div>
      <div class="card-body about-text">
        <h3 class="card-title">The spirit of real life recreational sport leagues brought to eSports</h3>
        <ul class="card-text">
          <li>Wecasual is a Dota 2 community that <b>hosts leagues and pick-up games</b> for players looking to have a fun and positive Dota 2 experience.</li>
          <li>Wecasual is a <b>toxic-player free environment</b> where players can play with a consistent team every week in our leagues and also
              participate in pick-up style games for those who want to play even more.</li>
          <li>There is no prize pool and there are no individual player rankings; Wecasual is strictly for those looking to hang out
          with friends and enjoy playing their games.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="card-title">Who is Wecasual for?</h3>
          <ul class="card-text">
            <li>We are looking for casual players whose primary objective is to have fun playing Dota 2.</li>
            <li>Our community is open to all players who are <b>less than 4k MMR </b> (Case by case exceptions can be made).</li>
            <li>Other than that, anyway can join Wecasual, as long as you are friendly person.</li>
            <li>We strongly encourage <b>newer players</b> to join!</li>

          </ul>

        <h3 class="card-title">How does Wecasual work?</h3>
          <ul class="card-text">
            <li><strike>To participate in the Wecasual community there is <b>$5/month subscription</b>.</strike></li>
            <h5>Wecasual is currently in a <b>Free Beta,</b> so players will have access to everything for free!</h5>
            <li>Wecasual has two main methods of play: the league and pick-up games</li>
            <li>Joining Wecasual requires you to play in the league on your team, but pick-up games are optional</li>
            <li><a href="/league-info">League detials</a></li>
            <li><a href="/pick-up-games">Pick-up game details</a></li>
          </ul>

        <h3 class="card-title">It's more than just Dota 2</h3>
          <ul class="card-text">
            <li>At Wecasual it is not just about playing Dota 2. Wecasual is the place to <span class="font-weight-bold">unwind and chill</span> out for people who love Dota 2.</li>
            <li>Before and after every game we offer activities to encourage players to <span class="font-weight-bold">hangout in our Discord</span> with their team and other teams too.</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="card-title">Discord Link</h3>
